  "hotBookmarks": [
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300014618_18_15534-15631",
      "chapterUid": 18,
      "range": "15534-15631",
      "markText": "居正在疏中虽请神宗恢弘圣度，但是居正的度量委实亟待恢弘。假如他认识吴中行等只是“迂儒拘挛之见”，那么为什么不能救解于事后？为什么认为上疏救解，只是欺世盗名之事？居正只是心地窄隘，谈不上容人之量。",
      "totalCount": 408,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300014618&chapterUid=18&rangeStart=15534&rangeEnd=15631",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/5c9321e0813ab6c35g018a18?chapterUid=18&rangeStart=15534&rangeEnd=15631"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300014618_16_547-637",
      "chapterUid": 16,
      "range": "547-637",
      "markText": "居正曾经自称别无他长，但能耐烦。这是一句谦虚的话，但是耐烦确是能使他成功的品德。耐烦的人对于一切事务有布置，有步骤。他不会一暴十寒，然而也不求一劳永逸，只是一步一步，脚踏实地去干。",
      "totalCount": 345,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300014618&chapterUid=16&rangeStart=547&rangeEnd=637",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/5c9321e0813ab6c35g018a18?chapterUid=16&rangeStart=547&rangeEnd=637"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300014618_9_15919-15953",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "15919-15953",
      "markText": "在严嵩的眼中，居正只是一个应酬诗文的作家，这又证实严嵩不如徐阶敏感。",
      "totalCount": 340,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300014618&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=15919&rangeEnd=15953",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/5c9321e0813ab6c35g018a18?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=15919&rangeEnd=15953"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300014618_9_1269-1320",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "1269-1320",
      "markText": "他是洞内的虎豹，发怒的时候会从洞内跳出来，打死些獐猫鹿兔，打得厌倦了，便仍回洞内，度那优裕懒散的生活。",
      "totalCount": 323,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300014618&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=1269&rangeEnd=1320",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/5c9321e0813ab6c35g018a18?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=1269&rangeEnd=1320"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300014618_9_6230-6302",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "6230-6302",
      "markText": "在居正入翰林院的时候，多数进士正在讨论怎样做西汉的文章和盛唐的诗句，但是居正的注意力却集中到实用上面。居正的目光似已远远地看到二十年以后的将来。",
      "totalCount": 306,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300014618&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=6230&rangeEnd=6302",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/5c9321e0813ab6c35g018a18?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=6230&rangeEnd=6302"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300014618_18_12624-12673",
      "chapterUid": 18,
      "range": "12624-12673",
      "markText": "居正伏着叩头道：“大众要我去，偏是皇上不许我走，我有什么办法？只要有一柄刀子，让我把自己杀了吧！”",
      "totalCount": 294,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300014618&chapterUid=18&rangeStart=12624&rangeEnd=12673",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/5c9321e0813ab6c35g018a18?chapterUid=18&rangeStart=12624&rangeEnd=12673"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300014618_13_23416-23500",
      "chapterUid": 13,
      "range": "23416-23500",
      "markText": "就在内阁里面，少保握起双拳，准备给少师一顿毒打，少傅、建极殿大学士张居正看不下去了，正要替他们劝解，冷不防少保也给少傅迎头一顿痛骂。真热闹，堂堂的内阁变成全武行的战场。",
      "totalCount": 288,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300014618&chapterUid=13&rangeStart=23416&rangeEnd=23500",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/5c9321e0813ab6c35g018a18?chapterUid=13&rangeStart=23416&rangeEnd=23500"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300014618_21_7952-7998",
      "chapterUid": 21,
      "range": "7952-7998",
      "markText": "国家到了艰难的时候，才想起往日的功臣。复官复荫，一切都是激励当时的臣工，但是事情已经太迟了。",
      "totalCount": 288,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300014618&chapterUid=21&rangeStart=7952&rangeEnd=7998",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/5c9321e0813ab6c35g018a18?chapterUid=21&rangeStart=7952&rangeEnd=7998"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300014618_12_23890-23942",
      "chapterUid": 12,
      "range": "23890-23942",
      "markText": "在继光镇守蓟州十六年当中，虽然没有赫赫的战绩，但是整个北边从此安静，这是继光的大功，当然也是居正的大功。",
      "totalCount": 272,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300014618&chapterUid=12&rangeStart=23890&rangeEnd=23942",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/5c9321e0813ab6c35g018a18?chapterUid=12&rangeStart=23890&rangeEnd=23942"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300014618_4_12466-12489",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "12466-12489",
      "markText": "努力啊，我愿有更好的成就，报答一切友好的关切。",
      "totalCount": 260,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300014618&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=12466&rangeEnd=12489",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/5c9321e0813ab6c35g018a18?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=12466&rangeEnd=12489"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300014618_9_5902-5971",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "5902-5971",
      "markText": "从此河套永远受着鞑靼骑士的蹂躏，却葬送了一个内阁大学士，一个总督陕西三边军务。严嵩复为首辅，再在那半清客、半权臣的局面下维持十五年的政权。",
      "totalCount": 255,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300014618&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=5902&rangeEnd=5971",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/5c9321e0813ab6c35g018a18?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=5902&rangeEnd=5971"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300014618_21_6389-6427",
      "chapterUid": 21,
      "range": "6389-6427",
      "markText": "有便，告知山西蒲州相公张凤盘，令张家事已完结矣，愿他辅佐圣明天子于亿万年也！",
      "totalCount": 252,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300014618&chapterUid=21&rangeStart=6389&rangeEnd=6427",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/5c9321e0813ab6c35g018a18?chapterUid=21&rangeStart=6389&rangeEnd=6427"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300014618_21_6744-6790",
      "chapterUid": 21,
      "range": "6744-6790",
      "markText": "经过多次拷问，敬修自缢身亡，懋修自杀未遂，居正十六年的政权，最后由敬修、懋修偿还这一笔血债。",
      "totalCount": 252,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300014618&chapterUid=21&rangeStart=6744&rangeEnd=6790",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/5c9321e0813ab6c35g018a18?chapterUid=21&rangeStart=6744&rangeEnd=6790"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300014618_9_6668-6757",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "6668-6757",
      "markText": "在不断的政治斗争中，居正在那里揣摩着：他知道在怎样的环境里，应当怎样维护自己。他也知道，在学习的期间，应当怎样地从容缓进。他和蜗牛一样，正在或左或右地伸出触角，寻觅政治上的支援。",
      "totalCount": 250,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300014618&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=6668&rangeEnd=6757",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/5c9321e0813ab6c35g018a18?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=6668&rangeEnd=6757"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300014618_12_21419-21448",
      "chapterUid": 12,
      "range": "21419-21448",
      "markText": "一切的计划都照准，一切困难都解决，在内阁中主持的全是居正。",
      "totalCount": 247,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300014618&chapterUid=12&rangeStart=21419&rangeEnd=21448",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/5c9321e0813ab6c35g018a18?chapterUid=12&rangeStart=21419&rangeEnd=21448"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300014618_9_17131-17168",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "17131-17168",
      "markText": "世宗任用严嵩，这是世宗的认识；继盛指摘严嵩的奸贼，便是指摘世宗的认识错误。",
      "totalCount": 240,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300014618&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=17131&rangeEnd=17168",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/5c9321e0813ab6c35g018a18?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=17131&rangeEnd=17168"
    },
